Package com.TeamNumberOne.canbusbackend.Controller

Class PacketManager

java.lang.Object
com.TeamNumberOne.canbusbackend.Controller.PacketManager
@CrossOrigin @Controller @RequestMapping(path="/packets") public class PacketManager extends Object
Creates a controller for the Packet model, this allows the population of data in the model, and allows the model to be modified without full access to the model for the end user.
